      <h1 data-content-field="title" class="entry-title p-name">
      
        <a href="/getreligion/2018/9/26/during-this-papal-in-flight-press-conference-the-news-was-what-francis-refused-to-discuss" class="u-url" rel="bookmark">Yo, scribes: During this papal in-flight presser, the news was what Francis refused to discuss</a>
      
      </h1>
      <div class="meta-below-title">
        
        <div class="entry-byline">
          <span class="entry-author"><a href="/?author=52cae7b0e4b01a6d175a55ab" class="p-author author entry-byline-link" rel="author">Terry Mattingly</a></span>
        </div>
        
