  <article class="entry h-entry hentry category-international-news category-terry-mattingly category-catholicism category-pope-francis category-godbeat category-vatican category-lgbtq tag-pope-francis tag-the-new-york-times tag-crux tag-pope-benedict-xvi tag-dubia tag-cardinal-walter-brandmller tag-bild tag-archbishop-carlo-maria-vigano author-terry-mattingly post-type-text article-index-6" id="article-5ba8e0d371c10b70170d912f" data-item-id="5ba8e0d371c10b70170d912f">

    <header class="entry-header">
      <div class="meta-above-title">
        
        <div class="entry-byline">
          <span class="entry-author"><a href="/?author=52cae7b0e4b01a6d175a55ab" class="p-author author entry-byline-link" rel="author">Terry Mattingly</a></span>
